Subject: Bluetooth: Add offload feature under experimental flag
Patch-mainline: v5.16-rc1
Git-commit: ad933151832855e3163e510a83716b8d20f3fae6
References: jsc#PED-1407

Allow user level process to enable / disable codec offload
feature through mgmt interface. By default offload codec feature
is disabled.

